code: import httpClient from'../common/http_common';import{httpClientPut,httpClientGet,httpClientDelete,httpClientPost}from'../common/http_common';var getAll=function getAll(){return httpClient.get("/places");};var getTopSix=function getTopSix(){return httpClient.get("/places/top-six");};var getByPage=function getByPage(page){var search=arguments.length>1&&arguments[1]!==undefined?arguments[1]:"";return httpClient.get("/places/page/".concat(page,"?search=").concat(search));};var createPlace=function createPlace(data){return httpClientPost.post("/places",data);};var getTop=function getTop(id){return httpClient.get("/places/top/".concat(id));};var get=function get(id){return httpClientGet.get("/places/detail/".concat(id));};var update=function update(id,data){return httpClientPut.put("/places/".concat(id),data);};var remove=function remove(id){return httpClientDelete.delete("/places/".concat(id));};var logger={getAll:getAll,get:get,getTopSix:getTopSix,getByPage:getByPage,createPlace:createPlace,remove:remove,update:update,getTop:getTop};export default logger;
